msgid "What we collect"
msgstr "Ce que nous collectons"

msgid ""
"We only require the minimum information that is necessary for matchmaking "
"and post-match contact: your name, email address, and your role (Ambassador "
"or Referee); additional information requested at registration is optional, "
"and is used only to improve the service: your phone number, nationality, "
